lead_paragraph: Matt Puempel hasn't really thought of himself as a goal scorer. After all, he'd only netted two goals in 24 games this season, and that tied a career high.

headline.print_headline: Puempel Gets Power-Play Hat Trick, Rangers Hold Off Coyotes
